# ==============================
# ABOUT
# ==============================

msgid "about_title"
msgstr "X-Ray Plugin"

msgid "about_text"
msgstr ""
"X-Ray Plugin\n"
"═══════════════════════════════\n"
"\n"
"WHAT DOES IT DO?\n"
"Enhances your books just like Amazon Kindle X-Ray!\n"
"Uses AI to automatically extract characters, locations,\n"
"historical context, and more.\n"
"\n"
"═══════════════════════════════\n"
"\n"
"FEATURES:\n"
"\n"
"Smart Menus\n"
"• Live counters on every menu item\n"
"• e.g. Characters (12), Locations (8)\n"
"\n"
"Multi-Language Support\n"
"• Turkish and English interface\n"
"• Language-specific data fetching from AI\n"
"• Easily add new languages\n"
"\n"
"Advanced Historical Analysis\n"
"• Captures direct references\n"
"• Detects indirect references\n"
"• Finds philosophical and intellectual contexts\n"
"\n"
"Better Feedback\n"
"• AI fetch time notifications\n"
"• Detailed progress messages\n"
"• Cache status reports\n"
"\n"
"═══════════════════════════════\n"
"\n"
"ALL FEATURES:\n"
"\n"
"AI Integration\n"
"• Google Gemini support (FREE!)\n"
"• ChatGPT support\n"
"• Smart JSON parsing\n"
"• Error compensation mechanism\n"
"\n"
"Character Management\n"
"• Automatic character extraction\n"
"• Detailed character profiles\n"
"• Gender, occupation, role info\n"
"• Character search feature\n"
"• Personal note-taking system\n"
"\n"
"Chapter Analysis\n"
"• Show current chapter characters instantly\n"
"• Character occurrence frequency\n"
"• Chapter-based filtering\n"
"\n"
"Timeline\n"
"• Chronological list of key events\n"
"• Event-character association\n"
"• Spoiler-free descriptions\n"
"\n"
"Historical Figures\n"
"• Detect real historical figures\n"
"• Biographical information\n"
"• Context within the book\n"
"• Birth-death dates\n"
"\n"
"Locations\n"
"• Important locations\n"
"• Location descriptions\n"
"• Importance in the story\n"
"\n"
"Themes and Summary\n"
"• List main themes\n"
"• Spoiler-free summary\n"
"• Author biography\n"
"\n"
"Cache System\n"
"• Automatic data saving\n"
"• Indefinitely valid\n"
"• Offline use\n"
"• Separate cache per book\n"
"\n"
"═══════════════════════════════\n"
"\n"
"QUICK START:\n"
"\n"
"1. Get API Key\n"
"Menu → X-Ray → AI Settings\n"
"→ Google Gemini API Key\n"
"(Free: makersuite.google.com)\n"
"\n"
"2. Fetch Data\n"
"Menu → X-Ray → Fetch AI Data\n"
"(Takes 10-15 seconds for the first time)\n"
"\n"
"3. Explore!\n"
"• Characters: See all characters\n"
"• This Chapter: Characters in the current chapter\n"
"• Timeline: Follow events\n"
"• Historical Figures: Real historical figures\n"
"\n"
"═══════════════════════════════\n"
"\n"
"SHORTCUTS:\n"
"\n"
"Alt + X : Quick X-Ray menu\n"
"Menu → X-Ray : Full menu\n"
"Long press Menu : Quick menu\n"
"\n"
"═══════════════════════════════\n"
"\n"
"TIPS:\n"
"\n"
"• Cache is created once, used forever\n"
"• Internet is only needed for the first fetch\n"
"• Character notes are saved per book\n"
"• Language change applies immediately\n"
"• Gemini Flash model is free and fast\n"
"\n"
"═══════════════════════════════\n"
"\n"
"TECHNICAL INFO:\n"
"\n"
"Cache Location:\n"
"~/.config/koreader/cache/xray/\n"
"\n"
"Settings Location:\n"
"~/.config/koreader/settings/xray/\n"
"\n"
"═══════════════════════════════\n"
"\n"
"EXAMPLE SCENARIOS:\n"
"\n"
"Reading Demons (Dostoevsky):\n"
" 15+ characters detected automatically\n"
" Historical figures like Sergei Nechayev added\n"
" 1860s Russia socialist movement explained\n"
" First appearances of characters marked\n"
"\n"
"Reading War and Peace (Tolstoy):\n"
" 100+ characters organized\n"
" Historical figures like Napoleon, Kutuzov\n"
" Events like Battle of Borodino in timeline\n"
" Locations like Moscow, Petersburg detailed\n"
"\n"
"Reading 1984 (Orwell):\n"
" Winston, Julia, O'Brien characters\n"
" Dystopian themes listed\n"
"• Chapter by chapter character tracking\n"
"• Analysis with personal notes\n"
"\n"
"═══════════════════════════════\n"
"\n"
"FAQ:\n"
"\n"
"Q: Is the API key free?\n"
"A: Yes! Gemini API has a free tier.\n"
"\n"
"Q: Is internet always required?\n"
"A: No, only for the first data fetch.\n"
"\n"
"Q: Where does the data come from?\n"
"A: From Google Gemini AI, based on the book title.\n"
"\n"
"Q: Does it give spoilers?\n"
"A: No, AI is trained to avoid spoilers.\n"
"\n"
"Q: Which languages are supported?\n"
"A: Currently Turkish and English. More can be added.\n"
"\n"
"Q: How do I clear cache?\n"
"A: Menu → X-Ray → Clear Cache\n"
"\n"
"═══════════════════════════════\n"
"\n"
"FEEDBACK:\n"
"\n"
"Share your suggestions and bug reports\n"
"on GitHub!\n"
"\n"
"═══════════════════════════════\n"
"\n"
"Happy reading!"

